<sect1 id="Annotator.ColorSeries">
	<title>Colour Concepts with Series Data</title>
	<para>
		Colours concepts according to a list of numerical attributes. The
		user can iterate over this list to select the attribute mapped to
		concept colour. For example, iterating through expression values of
		different time points of a micro-array experiment one after the other.
	</para>
